Text: When I try to extract the iso-file winrar says that there are files missing, what do I do?
When I try to extract the iso winrar tells me that there are archives missing, more specific, it tells me that the archive I've highlighted and extracting is missing, what do I do?

If you remove the (#) in each of the file names it should work fine.

So:
nnn-spatorrent-com (1).r00 --> nnn-spatorrent-com.r00
nnn-spatorrent-com (2).r01 --> nnn-spatorrent-com.r01
etc.
